<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Privacy Policy - Propload</title>
     <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/images/landing/Vector.jpeg">

    <!-- Tailwind before Bootstrap -->
    <link
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/tailwindcss/2.2.19/tailwind.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />

    <style>
      :root {
        --primary-color: #e9e2b3;
        --secondary-color: #2f6c7b;
      }

      .text-secondary {
        color: var(--secondary-color);
      }

      .bg-propload {
        background-color: var(--primary-color);
      }

      .bg-propload:hover {
        background-color: #dcd39e;
      }

      /* Animation for fade-in */
      @keyframes fadeInUp {
        0% {
          opacity: 0;
          transform: translateY(30px);
        }
        100% {
          opacity: 1;
          transform: translateY(0);
        }
      }

      .fade-in-up {
        opacity: 0;
        animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out forwards;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body class="bg-white min-h-screen flex flex-col">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="shadow-sm w-full px-20">
      <%- include('../partials/landingHeader') %>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <section
      class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-16 px-6 opacity-0 fade-in-up"
      style="animation-delay: 0.1s"
    >
      <h3 class="text-center text-secondary tracking-wide mb-2 font-semibold uppercase">
        Propload Privacy Policy: How We Protect Your Data and Privacy
      </h3>

      <h1
        class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-secondary text-center mb-12 fade-in-up"
        style="animation-delay: 0.3s"
      >
        Our Privacy Policy
      </h1>

      <div class="space-y-10 text-gray-700">
        <div class="fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.4s">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-secondary mb-2">1. Agreement Overview</h2>
          <p>
            By accessing and using our website, you agree to comply with the following
            terms and conditions. Please read these terms carefully before proceeding
            with any services on our platform.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.5s">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-secondary mb-2">2. Service Usage</h2>
          <p>
            Our platform allows customers to connect with qualified builders and
            service providers. You agree not to misuse the services or violate any
            applicable laws while using the platform.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.6s">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-secondary mb-2">3. Privacy Policy</h2>
          <p>
            Your privacy is important to us. Our Privacy Policy outlines how we collect,
            store, and manage your personal data when using our platform.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.7s">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-secondary mb-2">4. Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p>
            All content, images, and design elements on this site are the intellectual
            property of our company. Unauthorized use of this content is strictly
            prohibited.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.8s">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-secondary mb-2">5. Modifications</h2>
          <p>
            We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Users will be notified
            of any significant changes through the platform. Continued use of the platform
            after updates means you accept the new terms.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.9s">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-secondary mb-2">6. Governing Law</h2>
          <p>
            These terms and conditions are governed by the laws of [Your Country/State].
            Any disputes arising in connection with these terms shall be resolved under
            the jurisdiction of [Your Courts].
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <%- include('../partials/landingFooter') %>

    <!-- Trigger animation after load -->
    <script>
      document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => {
        const main = document.querySelector("section");
        main.classList.remove("opacity-0");
      });
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
